{"tid":760710,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴同情山神：人腳太廢 佢唔開心","createTime":"2018-07-29T18:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T23:38:41.000Z","uid":153867,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3da7f8b99858c41dbfb8dc89caa2c99e6614ee60","tid":760710,"uid":153867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:42:55.000Z","msg":"包括盧卡古在內等一眾「紅魔鬼」前線主力仍未歸隊，結果球隊終以1：4大敗予紅軍。作為隊中僅有的前線主力，山神賽後顯得十分沮喪，而摩帥亦直言理解。對於山神的情況，摩帥解釋：「看看他身邊的隊友，你覺得山齊士會開心嗎？我們在這裡根本不是找狀態或其他目的，只是想盡量不要輸得太難看。山神是陣中唯一的進攻球員，我們沒有翼鋒也沒有射手，就只有他一個在盡力踢。」<br />\n<br />\n不過摩帥隨後亦強調山神並沒有因隊友水平而「發脾氣」，「對AC米蘭時他表現很出色，我不認為他不開心。如果他不開心，他又如何連續兩仗都出長時間上陣兼有好表現？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48c79556f67e0f31209043d18642d6905eabdf8","tid":760710,"uid":79711,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:56:55.000Z","msg":"好難想像幫佢上陣既球員會點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n魔性澎湃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02dd768450a88308a7b28000f54aa4ab3ac5957c","tid":760710,"uid":31151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:57:16.000Z","msg":"賴連奴"},{"pid":"d262ef3c92c9ab749829fcd251e1fb972fc5e6d0","tid":760710,"uid":6327,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T19:07:47.000Z","msg":"阿狗人腳廢你又笑得咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68174c6c0faeacdf5e5d30e6de116e520ef2a1b","tid":760710,"uid":37240,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T19:50:19.000Z","msg":"領隊話自己